job_name = "CHAR_BLACK_WHIRLWIND"
description = "Li Kui, the Black Whirlwind. In the legend he fought with two axes and no fear and no brakes, loyal to his chief past all sense. Here a repo-collector of monstrous strength and wiped records, equal parts little brother and natural disaster. He loves the band with his whole heart. That is exactly the problem."
